# Lab 11 — OpenAI API Key Setup
#
# 1. Copy this file to `.env` in the project root:
#      cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Get your API key from OpenAI:
#      https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#
# 3. Paste your key below (no quotes needed):
#
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here
#
# --- Colab (optional) ---
# Add the same secret in Colab Secrets as OPENAI_API_KEY
# and enable notebook access. Example in the notebook:
#   os.environ["OPENAI_API_KEY"] = userdata.get("OPENAI_API_KEY")
